# Cursor Rules Template

## Effect-TS Patterns

This project uses Effect-TS. Effect patterns ship as skills under `.claude/skills/`,
loaded on demand by Claude Code.

Install the recommended starter set:

```bash
npx effect-claude-primitives --starter
```

List every available skill, or install a specific subset:

```bash
npx effect-claude-primitives --list
npx effect-claude-primitives --skills effect-error-handling,effect-concurrency
```

Install all skills:

```bash
npx effect-claude-primitives --all
```

